%N A334483 a(n) is the X-coordinate of the n-th point of the Sierpinski arrowhead curve; sequence A334484 gives Y-coordinates.
%C A334483 Coordinates are given on a hexagonal lattice with X-axis and Y-axis as follows:
%C A334483            Y
%C A334483           /
%C A334483          /
%C A334483         0 ---- X
%C A334483 The Sierpinski arrowhead curve can be represented using an L-system.
